com.i2group.apollo.externaldata.transport

Class RetrievalBlockAvailability

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.i2group.apollo.externaldata.transport.RetrievalBlockAvailability

  • public final class RetrievalBlockAvailability
extends Object
    A container for information about the availability of external sources when a request for information from them was made.

    The CardProvenances that are passed to a request in ProvenanceGroups contain RetrievalBlocks that refer to particular data sources. A RetrievalBlock that refers to a subset exploration service can be marked as "expired" if the item cache has timed out, or "unavailable" if the subset cannot be reached for any other reason.

    Since:
    4.0
